"aioseo-what-are-woocommerce-affiliate-plugins\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What are WooCommerce affiliate plugins?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>WooCommerce affiliate plugins allow you to set up and manage affiliate programs for your WooCommerce store. These tools can help you manage your affiliate network, track conversions, set commission rates, schedule payouts, and more.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-why-should-i-use-woocommerce-affiliate-plugins\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Why should I use WooCommerce affiliate plugins?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Using affiliate plugins helps you tap into the power of affiliate marketing to expand the reach and sales of your WooCommerce store. They can become lucrative sources of revenue and are easy to set up.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-can-you-sell-affiliate-products-on-woocommerce\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Can you sell affiliate products on WooCommerce?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Yes, you can sell affiliate products on WooCommerce. To add an affiliate product to your online store, follow these steps:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Open your WordPress dashboard.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Navigate to <strong>Products</strong> in the left sidebar menu.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Click <strong>Add New</strong>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Scroll down until you see the <strong>Product Data</strong> box.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Click on the dropdown menu that says <strong>Simple Product</strong> and change to <strong>External/Affiliate Product</strong>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Finish setting up your affiliate product, and you’re done!</li>\n</ol>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-how-do-i-add-an-affiliate-plugin-to-woocommerce\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">How do I add an affiliate plugin to WooCommerce?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Adding an affiliate plugin to WooCommerce is a straightforward process. After downloading and installing your chosen plugin, you can access it on your WordPress dashboard. From here, each plugin’s setup process will be slightly different. <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/plugins/how-to-easily-add-an-affiliate-program-in-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">This tutorial</a> does an excellent job explaining how to install 3 of the most popular WooCommerce affiliate plugins.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-propel-your-online-stores-growth-with-affiliate-plugins\">Propel Your Online Store’s Growth With Affiliate Plugins</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this article helped you understand how to leverage the best WooCommerce affiliate plugins on your online store. When you have the right one, the process is easy and makes for a diversified stream of income that doesn’t require much upkeep.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For more ideas on how to grow your WooCommerce store’s traffic and sales, you may enjoy reading other articles on our blog, like the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-woocommerce-plugins/\">best WooCommerce plugins</a> and our tutorial on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-product-review-schema-in-wordpress/\">adding product review schema in WordPress</a>. We also recommend this guide on <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/wordpress-security/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">WordPress security</a> to keep your website and clients’ data safe.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many tutorials on how to grow your WordPress site there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https