;s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50530:\"<p>Are you looking for the best on-page SEO tools for WordPress?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>On-page SEO is key for a successful content strategy. That’s because it takes the guesswork out of content creation and it maximizes your revenue.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;re going to share our picks for on-page SEO tools that’ll help you dethrone competitors as your content climbs the search engine rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-are-on-page-seo-tools-for-wordpress\">What are On-Page SEO Tools?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-the-best-on-page-seo-tools-for-wordpress-tested-and-compared\">The Best On-Page SEO Tools for WordPress: Tested and Compared</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-1-aioseo-all-in-one-seo\">1. AIOSEO (All in One SEO): Complete On-Page SEO Tool</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-2-monsterinsights-find-out-whats-working\">2. MonsterInsights: Find Out What&#8217;s Working</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-3-ahrefs-plan-content-that-ranks\">3. Ahrefs: Plan Content that Ranks</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-4-wprocket-speed-up-your-site\">4. WP Rocket: Speed Up Your Site</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-5-smashballoon-optimize-your-social-media-feeds\">5. SmashBalloon: Optimize Your Social Media Feeds</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-6-semrush-gain-competitive-advantage\">6. Semrush: Gain Competitive Advantage</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-google-search-console-performance-insights\">7. Google Search Console: Performance Insights</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-also-explore\">Also Explore</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-yoast-could-be-simpler\">Yoast SEO: Well-Known, Could be Simpler</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-rankmath-versatile-but-skip-the-content-ai\">Rank Math: Versatile, but Skip the ‘Content AI’</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-clearscope-create-content-that-outranks-competitors\">Clearscope: Create Content that Outranks Competitors</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-marketmuse-intelligent-content-planning\">MarketMuse: Intelligent Content Planning</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-screamingfrog-seo-spider-pro-level-diagnostics\">ScreamingFrog SEO Spider: Pro-Level Diagnostics</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-whats-the-best-on-page-seo-tool-for-wordpress\">What&#8217;s the Best On-Page SEO Tool for WordPress?</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-do-we-use\">What Do We Use?</a><ul></ul></li></ul></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-what-are-on-page-seo-tools-for-wordpress\">What are On-Page SEO Tools?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>On-page SEO tools are software products that analyze your content and provide recommendations to help it rank higher in SERPs (search engine results pages).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The best tools make hard SEO tasks as easy as clicking a button. And they can help you plan and write content that gets more conversions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;re going to focus on WordPress plugins but we’ll include a few online tools too.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-the-best-on-page-seo-tools-for-wordpress-tested-and-compared\">The Best On-Page SEO Tools for WordPress: Tested and Compared</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To help you whittle down the options, here&#8217;s our curated list of quality on-page SEO tools.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-1-aioseo-all-in-one-seo\">1. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"\">AIOSEO</a> (All in One SEO): Complete On-Page SEO Tool</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This SEO plugin has become a favorite of small businesses and bloggers because it makes SEO tasks easy. It&#8217;s racked up thousands of 5-star reviews on WordPress.org, and over 3 million people are currently using it.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"481\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-best-on-page-seo-tools-1024x481.png\" alt=\"aioseo homepage\" class=\"wp-image-144303\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-best-on-page-seo-tools-1024x481.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-best-on-page-seo-tools-300x141.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-best-on-page-seo-tools-768x361.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-best-on-page-seo-tools-600x282.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-best-on-page-seo-tools-128x60.png 128w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-best-on-page-seo-tools-191x90.png 191w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-best-on-page-seo-tools.png 1285w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO shines when it comes to on-page SEO thanks to its simple interface and clear instructions. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s easy to optimize on-page SEO basics, like title tags, meta descriptions, and focus keywords. And it shows you exactly what to do to optimize individual pages.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The plugin also analyzes your use of image alt tags and focus keyphrases and makes recommendations for improvements. (A focus keyphrase is the main keyword or topic that your article is about.)</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"982\" height=\"698\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-example.png\" alt=\"on-page seo tools\" class=\"wp-image-144244\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-example.png 982w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-example-300x213.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-example-768x546.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-example-600x426.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-example-84x60.png 84w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-example-127x90.png 127w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>AIOSEO&#8217;s recommendations include use of your focus keyword in headings and subheadings.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can see the plugin&#8217;s recommendations at the bottom of any WordPress page or post or in the right-hand sidebar menu.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"507\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/aioseo-general-settings-1024x507.jpg\" alt=\"aioseo sidebar\" class=\"wp-image-214673\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/aioseo-general-settings-1024x507.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/aioseo-general-settings-300x149.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/aioseo-general-settings-768x381.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/aioseo-general-settings-1536x761.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/aioseo-general-settings-2048x1015.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/aioseo-general-settings-600x297.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/aioseo-general-settings-121x60.jpg 121w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/aioseo-general-settings-182x90.jpg 182w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>AIOSEO&#8217;s recommendations cover readability too.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>One of our favorite features is the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-link-assistant-to-optimize-your-internal-linking-strategy/\">Link Assistant</a>. Link building is one of the most powerful SEO tactics, but it can be time-consuming and complicated.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Link Assistant shows you which pages on your site need more internal links. And it finds recommended articles to link from. It even selects a specific passage and anchor text to link on. All you have to do is click a button to add a link.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"583\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-link-assistant-1-1024x583.png\" alt=\"aioseo link assistant dashboard\" class=\"wp-image-166324\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-link-assistant-1-1024x583.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-link-assistant-1-300x171.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-link-assistant-1-768x437.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-link-assistant-1-600x341.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-link-assistant-1-105x60.png 105w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-link-assistant-1-158x90.png 158w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-link-assistant-1.png 1220w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO automatically generates <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/how-to-create-an-xml-sitemap/\">XML sitemaps</a> and provides HTML, RSS, and Google News sitemaps. The Pro version includes video sitemaps.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All in One SEO (AIOSEO) is a good choice for small businesses and bloggers who want a tool that&#8217;s easy to use and can get pro results.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Numerical SEO page score</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Headline Analyzer</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Local SEO for small businesses</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Click-button redirects</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Easy connection to webmaster tools</li>\n\n\n\n<li>SEO Analysis (site audit)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Click-to-add Schema markup for rich snippets</li>\n\n\n\n<li>ChatGPT and Google Search Console integration</li>\n\n\n\n<li>SEO revisions</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>AIOSEO</strong> <strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts at <a href=\"http://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"\">$49.60 per year</a>, free version <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/all-in-one-seo-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">available on WordPress.org</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Good to know</strong>: All in One SEO just launched a unique SEO revisions feature. This enables you to see the impact of your edits on your search engine rankings. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"497\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-search-statistics-1024x497.jpg\" alt=\"aioseo search statistics dashboard\" class=\"wp-image-196451\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-search-statistics-1024x497.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-search-statistics-300x146.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-search-statistics-768x373.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-search-statistics-1536x746.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-search-statistics-2048x994.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-search-statistics-600x291.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-search-statistics-124x60.jpg 124w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-search-statistics-185x90.jpg 185w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Find out how your content&#8217;s performing in Google with All in One SEO&#8217;s keyword rank tracking. </em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-theme-notice-box\" role=\"alert\">\n<p>Using <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/what-is-headless-wordpress-and-should-you-use-it/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">headless WordPress</a>? All in One SEO includes an integration with the WordPress <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/rest-api/\" title=\"\">REST API</a> to make SEO management easy.</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-2-monsterinsights-find-out-whats-working\">2. MonsterInsights: Find Out What&#8217;s Working</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">MonsterInsights</a> takes the guesswork out of analysis by showing you how your SEO actions are impacting your website results.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This plugin connects to Google Analytics and provides simple displays of your website&#8217;s most important data, including:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Revenue trends</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Which pages, forms, or pop-ups are converting the most people</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Average order value and top-selling products</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"636\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/monsterinsights-dashboard-1024x636.webp\" alt=\"monsterinsights dashboard\" class=\"wp-image-144240\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/monsterinsights-dashboard-1024x636.webp 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/monsterinsights-dashboard-300x186.webp 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/monsterinsights-dashboard-768x477.webp 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/monsterinsights-dashboard-1536x954.webp 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/monsterinsights-dashboard-2048x1272.webp 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/monsterinsights-dashboard-600x373.webp 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/monsterinsights-dashboard-97x60.webp 97w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/monsterinsights-dashboard-145x90.webp 145w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>MonsterInsights is a good complementary tool for SEO plugins like AIOSEO. Once you know what&#8217;s working, you can do more of it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Simple user interface</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Ecommerce tracking</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Track popularity of content, authors, tags, and categories</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Integrates with top plugins like <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">WPForms</a>, WooCommerce, and <a href=\"https://easydigitaldownloads.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">EasyDigitalDownloads</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>MonsterInsights</strong> <strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts at <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">$99.50 per year</a>. There is a <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-analytics-for-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">free version available</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-3-ahrefs-plan-content-that-ranks\">3. Ahrefs: Plan Content that Ranks</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Ahrefs</a> is an online tool designed to help you improve your search engine rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/ahrefs-homepage-1024x500.png\" alt=\"ahrefs homepage\" class=\"wp-image-144251\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/ahrefs-homepage-1024x500.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/ahrefs-homepage-300x147.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/ahrefs-homepage-768x375.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/ahrefs-homepage-600x293.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/ahrefs-homepage-123x60.png 123w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/ahrefs-homepage-184x90.png 184w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/ahrefs-homepage.png 1369w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s loaded with features to support smart content and outreach planning. These include a keyword research tool, referring domains data, and backlinks analysis. (<a href=\"https://aioseo.com/referring-domains-vs-backlinks-seo/\" title=\"\">Backlinks</a>, or links from other sites to yours, are a significant ranking factor. They’re sometimes referred to as “off-page SEO.”)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can pop an article URL into Ahrefs to see what organic keywords it’s ranking for. And you can discover which keywords your competitors are ranking for too.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Popular with marketing professionals, Ahrefs may also appeal to intermediate-level users looking for a keyword research tool to plan their content with.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ahrefs-keyword-difficulty-score-1-1024x309.png\" alt=\"ahrefs keyword overview \" class=\"wp-image-189640\" width=\"706\" height=\"213\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ahrefs-keyword-difficulty-score-1-1024x309.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ahrefs-keyword-difficulty-score-1-300x90.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ahrefs-keyword-difficulty-score-1-768x231.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ahrefs-keyword-difficulty-score-1-600x181.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ahrefs-keyword-difficulty-score-1-190x57.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ahrefs-keyword-difficulty-score-1-299x90.png 299w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ahrefs-keyword-difficulty-score-1.png 1221w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 706px) 100vw, 706px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Above: Using Ahrefs&#8217; Keyword Overview, we see that the keyword &#8220;what is a floating floor&#8221; is rated &#8220;6&#8221; or &#8220;Easy&#8221; to rank for. And it has an estimated monthly search volume of 1.2k.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Note: Ahrefs also has a free <a href=\"https://ahrefs.com/wordpress-seo-plugin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">WordPress plugin</a> designed to display SEO performance of your content and recommend content updates.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>SEO audit for content</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Monitor backlinks</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Traffic and page rank for each article</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Ahrefs</strong> <strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts at <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">$99/month</a>. The WordPress plugin is free.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-4-wprocket-speed-up-your-site\">4. WP Rocket: Speed Up Your Site</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Did you know that optimizing your <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/wordpress-performance-speed/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">site speed</a> is a form of SEO?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Search engines reward good user experience and penalize poor user experience. So it’s not surprising that website loading time is a ranking factor.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is where a caching plugin like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/wp-rocket\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">WP Rocket</a> comes in: you can speed up your site in minutes.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"575\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/wp-rocket-homepage-1024x575.png\" alt=\"wp rocket homepage\" class=\"wp-image-144253\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/wp-rocket-homepage-1024x575.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/wp-rocket-homepage-300x168.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/wp-rocket-homepage-768x431.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/wp-rocket-homepage-704x396.png 704w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/wp-rocket-homepage-600x337.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/wp-rocket-homepage-107x60.png 107w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/wp-rocket-homepage-160x90.png 160w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/wp-rocket-homepage.png 1397w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Tip: Check your site&#8217;s loading time, before and after WPRocket, in Google&#8217;s PageSpeed Insights.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Anyone who cares about increasing their traffic and conversions should make sure their site&#8217;s loading as fast as possible.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Page caching, browser caching, and pre-loading</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Minifies and combines CSS and JavaScript files</li>\n\n\n\n<li>File compression plus lazy loading of images</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>WPRocket Pricing:</strong> Starts at <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/wp-rocket\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">$59/year</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-5-smashballoon-optimize-your-social-media-feeds\">5. SmashBalloon: Optimize Your Social Media Feeds</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This is a beginner-friendly plugin that adds social media feeds to your WordPress website, the right way. The problem with social media feeds is they usually bog your site down.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://smashballoon.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">SmashBalloon</a> stands out because it optimizes all those ultra high-definition images in your feeds so they load fast. It also minimizes something called “external requests” and that speeds things up too. (To display a social feed, your website sends &#8220;requests&#8221; to that social media site.)</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"421\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/smashballoon-homepage-1024x421.jpg\" alt=\"smash balloon homepage\" class=\"wp-image-144255\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/smashballoon-homepage-1024x421.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/smashballoon-homepage-300x123.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/smashballoon-homepage-768x315.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/smashballoon-homepage-600x246.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/smashballoon-homepage-146x60.jpg 146w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/smashballoon-homepage-219x90.jpg 219w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/smashballoon-homepage.jpg 1378w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>SmashBalloon is fast and easy to use.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Boost SEO and CTR (click-through rates) with embedded social content</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Display multiple feeds</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Increase conversions with social media testimonials</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>SmashBalloon</strong> <strong>Pricing</strong>: Starts at <a href=\"https://smashballoon.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">$49/year</a> per plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-6-semrush-gain-competitive-advantage\">6. Semrush: Gain Competitive Advantage</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Semrush</a> is a standalone analysis tool for conducting keyword research and running site audits. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s similar to Ahrefs, and both are highly rated and widely used by content marketing professionals.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"453\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/semrush-homepage-1024x453.png\" alt=\"semrush homepage\" class=\"wp-image-144257\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/semrush-homepage-1024x453.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/semrush-homepage-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/semrush-homepage-768x340.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/semrush-homepage-600x265.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/semrush-homepage-136x60.png 136w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/semrush-homepage-204x90.png 204w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/semrush-homepage.png 1355w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Both tools will show you the keyword difficulty and search volume for a term. And you can use either tool to find long-tail, low-volume search terms that can help you win traffic that converts.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"564\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/semrush-keyword-overview-2-1-1024x564.png\" alt=\"semrush keyword overview\" class=\"wp-image-196343\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/semrush-keyword-overview-2-1-1024x564.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/semrush-keyword-overview-2-1-300x165.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/semrush-keyword-overview-2-1-768x423.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/semrush-keyword-overview-2-1-1536x846.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/semrush-keyword-overview-2-1-2048x1127.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/semrush-keyword-overview-2-1-600x330.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/semrush-keyword-overview-2-1-109x60.png 109w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/semrush-keyword-overview-2-1-163x90.png 163w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Semrush displays a Keyword Difficulty rating of &#8220;Easy&#8221; for &#8220;what is a floating floor.&#8221; The US (1k) and Global monthly search volume (2.1k) are also listed.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Like Ahrefs, Semrush has a free WordPress plugin, but it&#8217;s very different. The Semrush plugin is a &#8220;writing assistant&#8221; that makes suggestions for improving articles.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Semrush plugin is free. Full access to the online Semrush platform starts at $99.95/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Not a professional marketer? Don&#8217;t need a year&#8217;s worth of Semrush? You can cancel at any time.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Note: AIOSEO includes an integration with Semrush, to display related keywords for any given article.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Site audit</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Keyword recommendations</li>\n\n\n\n<li>SEO content templates</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Semrush</strong> <strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts at <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">$129.95/month</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-google-search-console-performance-insights\">7. Google Search Console: Performance Insights</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Google Search Console is an auxiliary tool that supports your SEO strategy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>When launching a new website, one of the first actions you&#8217;ll take is to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-submit-a-sitemap-to-google-wordpress-tutorial/\" title=\"\">submit the sitemap to Google</a>. And this is where you do that. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sitemap submission helps Google&#8217;s crawlers know when you publish new content or modify existing content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also inspect any URL on your site. Add it to the field at the top of Google Search Console to see if the page is indexed. You can click a button to request indexing.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"359\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/url-inspection-google-search-console-1024x359.png\" alt=\"google search console url inspection\" class=\"wp-image-196317\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/url-inspection-google-search-console-1024x359.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/url-inspection-google-search-console-300x105.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/url-inspection-google-search-console-768x269.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/url-inspection-google-search-console-600x210.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/url-inspection-google-search-console-171x60.png 171w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/url-inspection-google-search-console-257x90.png 257w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/url-inspection-google-search-console.png 1430w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>More importantly, GSC shows you how your content&#8217;s been performing in search results. Specifically, the Search Console Insights page provides</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Total clicks for the month</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Your most popular posts</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Which pages grew the most in traffic</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Insights also shows which search queries are responsible for the most click-throughs to your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Note that All in One SEO (AIOSEO) includes an integration with Google Search Console. So you can get this data right inside the WordPress dashboard.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This feature is available in the Elite version of the AIOSEO, which costs <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing\" title=\"\">$299.60/year</a> (the equivalent of $24.96/month).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So who is Google Search Console (GSC) for? Every site owner should have a GSC account. It’s indispensable for sitemap submission and site monitoring.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Its search performance metrics are valuable, and if you prefer to get these in WordPress, consider All in One SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Alerts for sitemap errors or manual penalties.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Click and search term metrics.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Insights into content performance.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Google Search Console</strong> <strong>Pricing</strong>: Free</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-also-explore\">Also Explore</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Below we&#8217;ve listed some well-regarded on-page SEO tools that you may also want to explore.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-yoast-could-be-simpler\">Yoast SEO: Well-Known, Could be Simpler</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/yoast\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Yoast SEO</a> is a well-known, all-purpose SEO plugin. It provides the standard on-page SEO tips for title tag and meta description length, as well as keyword (focus keyphrase) usage.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"481\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/yoast-interface-1024x481.png\" alt=\"yoast seo readability\" class=\"wp-image-144248\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/yoast-interface-1024x481.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/yoast-interface-300x141.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/yoast-interface-768x361.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/yoast-interface-600x282.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/yoast-interface-128x60.png 128w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/yoast-interface-192x90.png 192w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/yoast-interface.png 1112w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The interface seems a bit cramped compared to AIOSEO&#8217;s. And you&#8217;ll need to upgrade to Yoast&#8217;s Premium plugin to get recommendations on how to use your focus keyphrase to optimize your content for SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some may find Yoast&#8217;s product pricing page to be confusing: there are 11 different SEO plugins to choose from.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But this is a comprehensive SEO plugin with a strong track record. It will appeal to small businesses or bloggers interested in ease-of-use and results.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Emoji-based SEO score</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Semrush integration to find related keywords</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Schema markup for rich snippets</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Yoast SEO</strong> <strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts at <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/yoast\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">$99/year</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-rankmath-versatile-but-skip-the-content-ai\">Rank Math: Versatile, but Skip the ‘Content AI’</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Like AIOSEO, Rank Math provides snippet previews for your content and meta-tag analysis. But the display of title tags seems a bit nerdy to us: it includes bits of code called Regex. Beginners may wonder, &#8220;What do I do with this?&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"232\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/rankmath-title-tag-field-1024x232.png\" alt=\"rank math title field\" class=\"wp-image-144246\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/rankmath-title-tag-field-1024x232.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/rankmath-title-tag-field-300x68.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/rankmath-title-tag-field-768x174.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/rankmath-title-tag-field-600x136.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/rankmath-title-tag-field-190x43.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/rankmath-title-tag-field-397x90.png 397w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/rankmath-title-tag-field.png 1107w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Rank Math&#8217;s setup wizard is simpler than Yoast SEO&#8217;s but not as simple as AIOSEO&#8217;s.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A unique feature of <a href=\"https://rankmath.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Rank Math</a> is its &#8220;Content AI&#8221; tool, which provides recommendations to help your content rank higher. We tried it out on two articles: one that currently ranks in the #1 slot on Google for its keyword and one that currently ranks in the #2 slot for its keyword.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Rank Math&#8217;s Content AI gave both articles a <em>failing</em> grade.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We think Rank Math is a unique and versatile SEO plugin, but the Content AI tool needs work.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This plugin is a good fit for those who know Regex or aren&#8217;t afraid to learn how to use it. (It&#8217;s not hard.) Like All in One SEO (AIOSEO) and Yoast SEO, Rank Math is suitable for small businesses and bloggers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>On-page SEO recommendations</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Schema markup tool</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Content AI</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Rank Math</strong> <strong>Pricing</strong>: Starts at <a href=\"https://rankmath.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">$59/year.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-clearscope-create-content-that-outranks-competitors\">Clearscope: Create Content that Outranks Competitors</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.clearscope.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Clearscope</a> helps you plan and create high-quality content that gets more traffic.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"470\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/clearscope-homepage-1024x470.jpg\" alt=\"clearscope homepage\" class=\"wp-image-144259\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/clearscope-homepage-1024x470.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/clearscope-homepage-300x138.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/clearscope-homepage-768x353.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/clearscope-homepage-600x276.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/clearscope-homepage-131x60.jpg 131w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/clearscope-homepage-196x90.jpg 196w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/clearscope-homepage.jpg 1413w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You start by adding a target keyword to Clearscope, which runs a report on it. (New to keyword research? Check out <a href=\"https://www.blogtyrant.com/how-to-easily-find-the-best-keywords/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">this guide for beginners</a>.)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Using your keyword, Clearscope sifts through real-time Google data to provide clues to searcher intent. This is how the Clearscope report helps you create an article that is better organized, more helpful, and more comprehensive than your competitors&#8217;.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As with all digital tools, you need to use your judgment when it comes to assessing the page content recommendations and deciding what to do with them. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The need to use your judgment is highlighted by Clearscope&#8217;s occasional inclusion of recommended &#8220;terms&#8221; (subtopics) pulled from the <em>comments sections</em> of ranking articles or from alternate videos on YouTube pages.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Clearscope has a WordPress plugin, so you can get these content recommendations right in your WordPress editor. Realize though that you&#8217;ll need a Clearscope account for the WordPress plugin to work.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We think this tool is a good fit for professional content teams that need to scale.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Displays searcher questions related to a keyword</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Reveals themes present in top-ranking content on a given topic</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Content grading (up to &#8220;A++&#8221;)</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Clearscope</strong> <strong>Pricing</strong>: Starts at <a href=\"https://www.clearscope.io/pricing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">$170/month</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-marketmuse-intelligent-content-planning\">MarketMuse: Intelligent Content Planning</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>MarketMuse is AI-based software for planning and creating content that ranks. It&#8217;s also effective for building topical authority.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Add a keyword to <a href=\"https://www.marketmuse.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">MarketMuse</a> and it will pull data from related search results into a report that you can use to guide content creation.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"673\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/marketmuse-editing-pane-1024x673.png\" alt=\"marketmuse interface\" class=\"wp-image-196265\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/marketmuse-editing-pane-1024x673.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/marketmuse-editing-pane-300x197.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/marketmuse-editing-pane-768x505.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/marketmuse-editing-pane-1536x1010.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/marketmuse-editing-pane-2048x1346.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/marketmuse-editing-pane-600x394.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/marketmuse-editing-pane-91x60.png 91w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/marketmuse-editing-pane-137x90.png 137w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>A view of MarketMuse&#8217;s editorial pane with a closeup of some of the recommended topics.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And just as with Clearscope, you need to use your judgment when assessing any AI-based recommendations.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As you may have guessed, Clearscope and MarketMuse are competitors.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, MarketMuse has a unique advantage in that it analyzes your entire site and assigns topic authority and competitive advantage scores to your pages. As you do keyword research, you&#8217;ll see what your current topical authority is for that term.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This helps you prioritize which content to create. And it supports a <a href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/pillar-cluster-model-transform-blog\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">pillar and topic cluster</a> strategy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>MarketMuse is a good choice for content teams that need to scale. However, solopreneurs and bloggers can benefit from the free tier.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Competitive content analysis</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Keyword research that supports topical authority strategies</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Keyword difficulty score based on your existing content</li>\n\n\n\n<li>ChatGPT integration</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>MarketMuse Pricing</strong>: Starts at <a href=\"https://www.marketmuse.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">$149/month</a> for 1 user. Free version supports 1 user, 10 queries/month, limited page-level insights.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-screamingfrog-seo-spider-pro-level-diagnostics\">ScreamingFrog SEO Spider: Pro-Level Diagnostics</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.screamingfrog.co.uk/seo-spider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">ScreamingFrog</a> is a site audit tool for intermediate-level or advanced webmasters and do-it-yourselfers. It&#8217;s a website crawler (or &#8220;spider&#8221;) that analyzes your site’s URLs to find SEO issues that could affect user experience or ranking. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It provides dozens of metrics including</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>A complete list of internal and external links on your site</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Identification of broken links and security issues</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Duplicate content, including in title tags or meta descriptions.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"674\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/screamingfrog-dashboard-1024x674.jpg\" alt=\"screaming frog seo spider interface\" class=\"wp-image-196376\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/screamingfrog-dashboard-1024x674.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/screamingfrog-dashboard-300x197.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/screamingfrog-dashboard-768x505.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/screamingfrog-dashboard-1536x1010.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/screamingfrog-dashboard-600x395.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/screamingfrog-dashboard-91x60.jpg 91w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/screamingfrog-dashboard-137x90.jpg 137w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/screamingfrog-dashboard.jpg 2028w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This tool integrates with Google Analytics, Google PageSpeed Insights, and Google Search Console to deliver in-depth analysis of page-level performance issues.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Website designers and professional marketers use this tool to analyze site structure. And it&#8217;s often used by website project managers when migrating a site to a new platform.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Site architecture visualization</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Hreflang attribute auditing</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Structured data validation</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Integration with Ahrefs, Majestic, and Moz</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Screaming Frog SEO Spider Pricing:</strong> Starts at <a href=\"https://www.screamingfrog.co.uk/seo-spider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">free</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-whats-the-best-on-page-seo-tool-for-wordpress\">What&#8217;s the Best On-Page SEO Tool for WordPress?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For simplicity and power, we think it&#8217;s hard to beat the AIOSEO plugin. It has everything you need for on-page SEO and provides more sitemap types than Yoast SEO or RankMath.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Unlike Yoast, it provides focus keyphrase recommendations without requiring users to upgrade to a pricier plugin. And unlike RankMath, the setup wizard is a breeze with its minimal steps.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We think that MonsterInsights is a must-have for easy measurement.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You may have heard that SEO professionals are now charging as much as 5 or 6 figures a year per client. So these 2 tools can save you money.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-what-do-we-use\">What Do We Use?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We use <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing\" title=\"\">AIOSEO</a> and <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">MonsterInsights</a> for on-page SEO coupled with <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">WPForms</a> and <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">OptinMonster</a> for conversions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>These 4 WordPress plugins have the benefit of being beginner-friendly but powerful enough to deliver results for pros. They&#8217;re a good fit for DIY site owners including small businesses, affiliate marketers, agencies, or bloggers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>These tools have helped us to consistently grow our traffic and revenue, month after month.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We think you deserve the same success too.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Lastly, because we need to scale across multiple content teams while maintaining quality and competitive advantage, we also use Semrush, Ahrefs, and Clearscope.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ultimately, you&#8217;ll decide what works best for you in the context of your work. &#8220;Best” often really means “recommended.” The on-page SEO tools we’ve discussed are world class. And “best” is often subjective.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-qa-for-on-page-seo\">FAQs Related to On-Page SEO Tools</h2>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-whats-the-difference-between-technical-seo-and-seo\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What’s the difference between technical SEO and SEO?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>The term &#8220;technical SEO&#8221; is used by writers to refer to an aspect of SEO that they think requires specialized knowledge. It&#8217;s a subjective term, similar to &#8220;advanced SEO.&#8221; By contrast, &#8220;SEO&#8221; refers to the entire field of search engine optimization. As such, discussion of SEO may include material suited to beginners, intermediate-level learners, or digital marketing professionals.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-whats-the-difference-between-on-page-seo-and-off-page-seo\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What&#8217;s the difference between on-page SEO and off-page SEO?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>&#8220;On-page SEO&#8221; refers to aspects of a web page that impact SEO and that you have control over. These elements include page loading speed, content quality, logical structure, title tag, meta description, image and video alt tags, Schema markup, and effective use of a targeted keyword.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;Off-page SEO&#8221; refers to backlinks (links from other websites to yours), which are a significant ranking factor, as well as non-linked guest posts and brand mentions on other sites.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-free-seo-tools-do-you-recommend\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What free SEO tools do you recommend?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>The AIOSEO Analyzer is a <a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/all-in-one-seo-analyzer-b/gdmkcblhddhhfejpfbjomilpgpbpjhhg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">free Chrome extension</a> that you can use to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ten-ways-to-use-the-aioseo-analyzer-chrome-extension/\" title=\"\">speed up SEO checks</a>. In addition, we recommend the free <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-analyzer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">AIOSEO SEO Analyzer</a> to conduct a full site audit. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ahrefs has a <a href=\"https://ahrefs.com/seo-toolbar\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">free toolbar</a> that is an on-page SEO checker. It provides SEO metrics for pages you visit, including keyword difficulty, search volume and SERP positions. You can also get an SEO report for any page. Intermediate and advanced site owners may be interested in the canonical URL check and the information on directives for crawlers found in HTTP headers and meta tags.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We also like SerpRobot’s <a href=\"https://www.serprobot.com/serp-check\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">free SERP checker.</a> You can use it to find out the page ranking of an article.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-i-cant-afford-clearscope-can-you-recommend-an-alternative\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">I can&#8217;t afford Clearscope. Can you recommend an alternative?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>While content analysis tools like Clearscope are popular with teams that run more than one website, many site owners need to do more with less. We get it. Here&#8217;s an alternative approach that we&#8217;ve tested and used to land top slots in Google and snag the featured snippet for our target keywords.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Use long tail keywords</strong>: When choosing a keyword (main topic) to base an article on, use a <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/long-tail-keywords/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">long tail keyword</a>. It’s much easier to rank for long tails because there’s less competition. Long tails also typically drive less traffic, but here’s the thing: because these keywords contain more information (i.e., they’re detailed phrases), they tend to drive a higher quality of traffic, which typically results in more conversions.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Scout out the competition</strong>: Do a <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-secrets-to-grow-revenue/#aioseo-1-produce-high-quality-content-that-aligns-with-search-intent\" title=\"\">search in Chrome Incognito</a> for your target keyword, to see what you&#8217;re up against. Scan page 1 of search results. Note any hints of related questions searchers have or problems they&#8217;re trying to solve. Consider addressing some of those issues in your article. That can make the article more useful to the readers.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Focus on quality</strong>: Google’s algorithm rewards quality, so be sure to do your best. Take time to create an outline first. That will help you stay organized. Then write an article that’s more helpful or interesting to your reader than the top-ranking ones. (“More helpful” can include being easier to understand or more comprehensive than competing pages.) Review and revise your article a few times before publishing.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>And don’t forget to check your on-page SEO.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-next-action-steps\">Next Action Steps</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A good SEO strategy includes on-page optimization, new content creation, and improving your existing content. Our list of the best SEO tools will help you achieve these goals.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you understand what on-page SEO tools can do for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You may also want to check out our article on the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-product-review-plugins/\">best product review plugins</a> and how to use <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-wordpress-faq-block-to-boost-seo-and-get-more-traffic/\">WordPress FAQ blocks</a> to snatch market share from your competitors.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find lots of helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-on-page-seo-tools/\">Best On-Page SEO Tools for WordPress (Tested and Reviewed)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:47:\"https://aioseo.com/best-on-page-seo-tools/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"How to Set SEO Goals that Help Boost Rankings [Beginner’s Guide]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:144:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-set-seo-goals-that-boost-rankings/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=how-to-set-seo-goals-that-boost-rankings\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-set-seo-goals-that-boost-rankings/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 15 Aug 2023 16:40:11 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"SEO Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"seo goals\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"SEO tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"setting seo goals\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=218357\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:438:\"<p>Would you like to know how to set SEO goals that result in better rankings? Setting goals for your SEO campaigns helps you know what you’re working towards and gives you a clear direction on the steps to take. In&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-set-seo-goals-that-boost-rankings/\">How to Set SEO Goals that Help Boost Rankings [Beginner’s Guide]</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20682:\"<p>Would you like to know how to set SEO goals that result in better rankings?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Setting goals for your SEO campaigns helps you know what you’re working towards and gives you a clear direction on the steps to take.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we’ll show you how to set meaningful SEO goals to help you drive your business forward.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-are-seo-goals\">What are SEO Goals?</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-is-setting-seo-goals-important\">Is Setting SEO Goals Important?</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-set-seo-goals-in-5-easy-steps\">How to Set SEO Goals in 5 Easy Steps</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-1-have-the-right-seo-tools\">1. Have the Right SEO Tools</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-2-be-s-m-a-r-t\">2. Be S.M.A.R.T</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-3-start-with-the-outcome\">3. Start with the Outcome</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-4-outline-the-process\">4. Outline the Process</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-5-determine-your-key-performance-indicators-kpis\">5. Determine Your Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-seo-goals-5-examples-and-how-to-achieve-them\">SEO Goals: 5 Examples and How to Achieve Them</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-1-boost-brand-awareness\">1. Boost Brand Awareness</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-2-increase-organic-traffic\">2. Increase Organic Traffic</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-3-increase-organic-clickthrough-rate-ctr\">3. Increase Organic Clickthrough Rate (CTR)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-4-decrease-your-bounce-rate\">4. Decrease Your Bounce Rate</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-5-increase-your-revenue\">5. Increase Your Revenue</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-are-seo-goals\">What are SEO goals?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-why-are-seo-goals-important\">Why are SEO goals important?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-do-i-measure-the-success-of-my-seo-goals\">How do I measure the success of my SEO goals?</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-setting-seo-goals-is-critical-to-your-success\">Setting SEO Goals is Critical to Your Success</a></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-what-are-seo-goals\">What are SEO Goals?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>SEO goals are objectives you aim to achieve through your SEO campaigns over a period of time. Each goal should contribute to the overall purpose of your SEO and help you reach your business goals.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In short, your SEO goals should help you reach more prospective users through organic search. Your SEO goals should also help you turn website visitors into customers or subscribers.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-is-setting-seo-goals-important\">Is Setting SEO Goals Important?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Setting SEO goals is important as it helps focus on the necessary SEO tasks that get you results. It also helps bring clarity to your campaign. This way, everything you do is bound to produce better results.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Running your SEO campaigns without any goals is like shooting in the dark. You don’t know what you’ll hit. And even if you hit something, it may not be the result you’re looking for.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, to run impactful SEO campaigns, you should set common-sense SEO goals.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-to-set-seo-goals-in-5-easy-steps\">How to Set SEO Goals in 5 Easy Steps</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready to set impactful SEO goals? Let’s dig into some tips.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-1-have-the-right-seo-tools\">1. Have the Right SEO Tools</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the first steps to succeeding in setting and achieving your SEO goals is to have the right tools. And one of the best and most versatile SEO tools is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"311\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO is one of the best SEO plugins on the market and can help you set and monitor SEO goals.\" class=\"wp-image-151544\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-600x267.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">AIOSEO</a> is the best WordPress SEO plugin on the market and has been downloaded over 100 million times. Millions of savvy website owners and marketers trust the plugin to help them dominate <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-are-serps/\" title=\"What Are SERPs (And Why Are they Important to SEO)?\">search engine results pages</a> (SERPs) and drive relevant traffic to their sites. This plugin has many <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/\" title=\"Features\">powerful SEO features and modules</a> to help you optimize your website for search engines and users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>When setting and monitoring your SEO goals, AIOSEO has features like SEO Analysis and Search Statistics to help you get the essential data you need to run impactful campaigns.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For step-by-step instructions on how to install AIOSEO, check out our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\" title=\"Installing All in One SEO Pro\">installation guide</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-2-be-s-m-a-r-t\">2. Be S.M.A.R.T</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the first steps to setting common-sense SEO goals is to be S.M.A.R.T. This means when you set your SEO goals, they should be:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Specific</strong>: Your SEO goals must be specific, not generic. It helps you prove that your optimization efforts are working.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Measurable</strong>: You should be able to assign key performance indicators (KPIs) to your goals.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Actionable</strong>: Ensure you can take actionable steps that can impact the KPIs.&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Relevant</strong>: Every SEO goal should be relevant to your marketing and business objectives.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Time-bound</strong>: Include time-related parameters to help you keep track of your progress.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Knowing how to set S.M.A.R.T. SEO goals is critical to running successful campaigns. It helps you manage expectations and be in control of your progress.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-3-start-with-the-outcome\">3. Start with the Outcome</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Consider your outcome as the endgame: what you want to achieve.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To set common-sense SEO goals, you need to look at the ultimate goal of your SEO campaign and the timeframe you want to achieve it in. It should align with your business goals and contribute to your overall success.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the best ways to paint a clear picture of the outcome is to look at important issues like:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Mission statement</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Analyze issues that hinder conversions</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Marketing and sales problems you encounter the most</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Using insights like these, you can better set meaningful goals for your business.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-4-outline-the-process\">4. Outline the Process</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you’ve defined the outcome, the next step to setting your SEO goals is to outline the processes needed to achieve your objective. Doing this helps you break down your outcome into smaller, manageable performance goals. These are the short-term wins that bring you closer to the ultimate goal.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, your goal is to rank within the top 3 on SERPs for a keyword. In this case, you could break down the process into:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-copywriting/\" title=\"10 Best SEO Copywriting Tips for Crafting Content that Converts\">Creating optimized content</a> around your keyword</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Implementing an <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-link-assistant-to-optimize-your-internal-linking-strategy/\" title=\"How to Use Link Assistant to Optimize Your Internal Linking Strategy\">internal linking strategy</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/link-building-guide/\" title=\"The Ultimate Link Building Guide You Need for 2023\">Building backlinks</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>These processes can be turned into individual S.M.A.R.T SEO goals that can help you reach the ultimate goal of ranking in the top 3 spots on SERPs.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-5-determine-your-key-performance-indicators-kpis\">5. Determine Your Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another critical step to setting impactful SEO goals is determining key performance indicators (KPIs). KPIs are the metrics you use to measure the performance of your goals. Examples of KPIs you can use include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Traffic</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Average clickthrough rate (CTR)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Search impressions</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Number of clicks</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Position (ranking)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Revenue from organic traffic</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>You’ll need some SEO monitoring tools to help you measure these KPIs. One such tool you can use right within WordPress is AIOSEO’s Search Statistics module. This is our Google Search Console (GSC) integration and gives you a lot of insights into your search performance.   </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"387\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seo-goals-search-statistics-dashboard.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO\'s Search Statistics gives you a lot of SEO data you can use to set SEO goals.\" class=\"wp-image-218366\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seo-goals-search-statistics-dashboard.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seo-goals-search-statistics-dashboard-300x165.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seo-goals-search-statistics-dashboard-600x331.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seo-goals-search-statistics-dashboard-109x60.png 109w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seo-goals-search-statistics-dashboard-163x90.png 163w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also use Search Statistics to help you <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/search-statistics-power-hacks-to-help-boost-your-rankings/\" title=\"6 Search Statistics Power Hacks to Help Boost Your Rankings\">achieve your SEO goals</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-seo-goals-5-examples-and-how-to-achieve-them\">SEO Goals: 5 Examples and How to Achieve Them</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you know how to set common-sense SEO goals, let’s quickly look at some of the common ones you can set for your business. We’ll also look at some tips for achieving them.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-1-boost-brand-awareness\">1. Boost Brand Awareness</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Brand awareness refers to the extent to which your target audience is familiar with your brand or products. It’s essential in gaining user trust and results in increased sales. SEO is a fantastic way of boosting brand awareness. Here’s an example of an SEO goal that helps you do this:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><em>Achieve first-page ranking for [keyword] within 12 months</em></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides checking your position on SERPs, you can also measure this goal by the month-on-month (MoM) increase in Search Impressions.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"462\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seo-goals-search-impressions.png\" alt=\"Search Impressions help you see if your brand is getting visibility on SERPs.\" class=\"wp-image-218367\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seo-goals-search-impressions.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seo-goals-search-impressions-300x197.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seo-goals-search-impressions-600x395.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seo-goals-search-impressions-91x60.png 91w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seo-goals-search-impressions-137x90.png 137w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Search Impressions measure the number of times your search listing is seen on SERPs. An increase indicates that more people are noticing your content. It also shows that your listing is rising up in rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-2-increase-organic-traffic\">2. Increase Organic Traffic</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the most common SEO goals is increasing organic traffic to your site. Remember, your goals must be S.M.A.R.T, so just saying you want to increase organic traffic won’t cut it. You should also state how much traffic increase you want and specify the time frame. Here’s an example:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><em>Increase organic traffic by 20% in 4 months</em></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>How can you do that?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are a few manageable goals you can set to help you achieve that:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Publish X optimized pieces of content every month</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Build X backlinks on reputable publications</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Share each post X times on social media every week</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-3-increase-organic-clickthrough-rate-ctr\">3. Increase Organic Clickthrough Rate (CTR)</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another SEO goal you can set is increasing your clickthrough rates (CTRs). CTR refers to the percentage of people who click on your search listing on SERPs.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"473\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seo-goals-average-ctr.png\" alt=\"Your average CTR helps you see if you\'re meeting your SEO goals.\" class=\"wp-image-218374\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seo-goals-average-ctr.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seo-goals-average-ctr-300x202.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seo-goals-average-ctr-600x404.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seo-goals-average-ctr-89x60.png 89w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seo-goals-average-ctr-134x90.png 134w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So what would this SEO goal look like?</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><em>Increase organic CTR by 5% in 3 months</em></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>A few tips to help you achieve this goal include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-check-if-your-google-search-snippets-are-properly-optimized/\" title=\"How to Check If Your Google Search Snippets Are Properly Optimized\">Optimize your SERP snippets</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Craft click-worthy <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-title-tags/\" title=\"How to Write Killer SEO Title Tags: 8 Simple Tips\">SEO titles</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Enhance your search snippets with <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-create-jump-links-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Create Jump Links in WordPress (and Increase Your Visibility On SERPs)\">jump links</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>For more tips on reaching your goal to increase your CTR, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ways-to-increase-your-organic-clickthrough-rates/\">check out this guide</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-4-decrease-your-bounce-rate\">4. Decrease Your Bounce Rate</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Bounce rate is the percentage of site visitors who leave after viewing one page rather than continuing to view other pages on your site. A high bounce rate indicates your website design or content doesn’t meet users&#8217; needs. As a result, you lose out on valuable traffic.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some examples of how you would set a goal to decrease the bounce rate:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Reduce bounce rate by 15% in 5 months</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Reduce bounce rate to 55% in 6 months</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some tips for reducing your bounce rate include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Improving your <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/10-quick-easy-ways-to-speed-up-your-site/\" title=\"10 Ways to Speed up Your WordPress Site\">page load speed</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>A user-friendly site design</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Content that meets search intent</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Strategic <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ways-link-assistant-can-save-you-time-on-internal-and-external-link-building/\" title=\"6 Ways Link Assistant Can Save You Time On Internal Link Building\">internal linking</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Find out <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/user-behavior-analytics-in-seo/\" title=\"4 Ways User Behavior Analytics can Help Guide Your SEO Strategy\">what users want</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>A lower bounce rate means people are consuming your content. This results in improved sales and newsletter subscriptions. It also leads to more returning visitors, an important element in building an engaged audience.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-5-increase-your-revenue\">5. Increase Your Revenue</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The ultimate business goal of SEO is to drive revenue. After all, as a marketing channel, you want your SEO strategy to help you generate leads and increase your customer base. Here’s a hypothetical example of an SEO goal that directly impacts your revenue:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><em>Increase revenue by 10% in the next three months</em></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>A few ways you can use SEO to help you achieve this include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Create bottom-of-the-funnel (BoFu) content</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Leverage SEO reputation management to build authority and gain trust</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Maximize your <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/a-complete-local-seo-checklist/\" title=\"A Complete Local SEO Checklist: 10 Tips to Improve Rankings\">local SEO</a> </li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>SEO Goals: Your FAQs Answered</p>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-are-seo-goals\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\"><strong>What are SEO goals?</strong></h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>SEO goals refer to the specific objectives and outcomes a website or online business aims to achieve through search engine optimization (SEO) efforts. These goals are typically aligned with improving the website&#8217;s visibility, organic traffic, and overall performance on search engine results pages (SERPs).</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-why-are-seo-goals-important\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\"><strong>Why are SEO goals important?</strong></h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Setting clear SEO goals helps provide direction and focus to your optimization efforts. Without well-defined goals, it&#8217;s challenging to measure the effectiveness of your strategies and determine whether your SEO efforts are producing desired results.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-how-do-i-measure-the-success-of-my-seo-goals\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\"><strong>How do I measure the success of my SEO goals?</strong></h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>If you&#8217;re a WordPress user, tools like All In One SEO (AIOSEO) can help you measure key performance indicators (KPIs) that help you track the success of your SEO goals. </p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-setting-seo-goals-is-critical-to-your-success\">Setting SEO Goals is Critical to Your Success</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>SEO is a powerful channel that can help you grow your business and increase revenue, especially if you set the right SEO goals. Unfortunately, many small business owners never set goals for their campaigns, resulting in them not getting the desired results.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this article has helped you learn how to set common-sense SEO goals. You can also check out other articles on our blog, like our guide to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-stop-content-decay-and-regain-lost-traffic/\" title=\"How to Stop Content Decay and Regain Lost Web Traffic (Easy SEO Guide)\">spotting and stopping content decay</a> or our tutorial on monitoring the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-monitor-the-impact-of-google-algorithm-updates-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Monitor the Impact of Google Algorithm Updates in WordPress\">impact of Google algorithm updates</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-set-seo-goals-that-boost-rankings/\">How to Set SEO Goals that Help Boost Rankings [Beginner’s Guide]</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-set-seo-goals-that-boost-rankings/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\"